resource policy on the boot disk
(crash-consistent, whole disk)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#eef3fb,#1f2a38);strokeColor=#5A6B7B;fontColor=#1A1A1A;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" parent="ops"><mxGeometry x="468" y="60" width="239" height="98" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="absent" value="EXPLICITLY ABSENT — do not assume:
• NO CDN (no Cloud CDN, no Cloudflare)
• NO cloud load balancer — DNS A records resolve
   straight to the VM's static external IP
• NO managed database (Postgres runs in a container)
• NO Cloud Storage / R2 — object storage is self-hosted MinIO
• NO container registry — images are built on the VM
• NO VPC peering / Cloud NAT / Cloud Armor / GKE
• Single zone, single VM — no HA, no autoscaling" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#f8cecc,#5a2b28);strokeColor=#B85450;fontColor=#1A1A1A;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" parent="band_gcp"><mxGeometry x="833" y="38" width="260" height="188" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="ed1" value="resolve cverify.com.vn" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;html=1;rounded=0;jettySize=auto;orthogonalLoop=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=light-dark(#1B2733,#CFE0F0);strokeColor=light-dark(#2D6A9F,#5B9BD5);strokeWidth=2;labelBackgroundColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#0B0F14);exitX=1;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="user_browser" target="dns"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="342" y="252"/><mxPoint x="342" y="277"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="ed2" value="A record → static IP (no proxy)" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;html=1;rounded=0;jettySize=auto;orthogonalLoop=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=light-dark(#1B2733,#CFE0F0);strokeColor=light-dark(#2D6A9F,#5B9BD5);strokeWidth=2;labelBackgroundColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#0B0F14);exitX=0;exitY=0.3;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="dns" target="eip"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="390" y="528"/><mxPoint x="348" y="528"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="ed3" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;html=1;rounded=0;jettySize=auto;orthogonalLoop=1;fontSize=10;fontColor=light-dark(#1B2733,#CFE0F0);strokeColor=light-dark(#2D6A9F,#5B9BD5);strokeWidth=2;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="eip" target="fw"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="ed4" value="tcp/80,443 · tcp/22 (restricted)" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;html=1;rounded=0;jettySize=auto;orthogonalLoop=1;fontSize=10;fontCo